354
00:13:37,940 --> 00:13:39,140
I was going to ask,

355
00:13:39,300 --> 00:13:41,100
where did you get

356
00:13:41,100 --> 00:13:42,140
the 400 thousand penalty?

357
00:13:42,260 --> 00:13:42,780
Xiaohu.

358
00:13:47,100 --> 00:13:47,460
Here.

359
00:13:51,740 --> 00:13:53,380
You're so bold.

360
00:13:53,620 --> 00:13:54,820
You three schemed together,

361
00:13:54,820 --> 00:13:56,260
without telling me and Xiaotao.

362
00:13:56,260 --> 00:13:57,820
Don't you see us as part of the team?

363
00:13:57,830 --> 00:13:58,990
You should be punished with drinks.

364
00:13:59,020 --> 00:13:59,340
Yes.

365
00:13:59,340 --> 00:13:59,700
Exactly.

366
00:13:59,940 --> 00:14:00,580
All of you.

367
00:14:00,820 --> 00:14:01,380
Drink.

368
00:14:02,060 --> 00:14:03,140
We're sorry.

369
00:14:03,380 --> 00:14:04,140
Actually,

370
00:14:04,140 --> 00:14:05,740
we wanted to surprise you.

371
00:14:06,420 --> 00:14:07,580
Now that we have the money,

372
00:14:07,980 --> 00:14:08,500
we can

373
00:14:08,620 --> 00:14:10,580
open a department store.

374
00:14:10,710 --> 00:14:12,460
This deal was made possible
because of you.

375
00:14:12,740 --> 00:14:13,420
So

376
00:14:13,580 --> 00:14:15,340
Young Master and I
would like to invite you

377
00:14:15,340 --> 00:14:16,300
to be our partner.

378
00:14:16,900 --> 00:14:17,380
Really?

379
00:14:17,460 --> 00:14:18,100
Really.

380
00:14:18,660 --> 00:14:19,500
From now on,

381
00:14:19,700 --> 00:14:21,260
you'll be our owner

382
00:14:21,540 --> 00:14:22,900
Great.

383
00:14:25,540 --> 00:14:26,780
Then I'm not mad anymore.

384
00:14:27,060 --> 00:14:27,900
Thank you, Wanyue.

385
00:14:28,580 --> 00:14:29,820
Thank you, Mr. Zhang.

386
00:14:30,940 --> 00:14:32,460
Thank you, Miss Gu.

